query:
SELECT a.*, v.id as volante_existe, v.nome as volante_nome, v.telegramChatId 
FROM agendamentos_volante a
LEFT JOIN volantes v ON a.volanteId = v.id
WHERE DATE(a.data) = '2026-02-13';
